WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.778
We operate in an environment where technological acceleration directly causes

00:00:04.778 --> 00:00:09.556
cultural friction. The traditional rulebooks of management are obsolete. The

00:00:09.556 --> 00:00:14.335
focus here is the bottom line and immediate, strict practical

00:00:14.335 --> 00:00:19.113
relevance to the complex social systems encountered daily. A performance

00:00:19.113 --> 00:00:23.891
of understanding means actively applying, analyzing, and creating new knowledge

00:00:23.891 --> 00:00:28.669
to solve undefined challenges. Let us look at a simple

00:00:28.669 --> 00:00:33.447
A vs B judgment. Option A: A leader memorizes management

00:00:33.447 --> 00:00:38.225
theories but struggles to resolve a team dispute. Option B:

00:00:38.225 --> 00:00:43.004
A leader actively applies a new communication strategy to resolve

00:00:43.004 --> 00:00:47.782
the dispute. Option B is the correct approach because true

00:00:47.782 --> 00:00:52.560
learning only occurs through practical application in real-world scenarios.
